ming.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Bolis-Pupul-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/bolis-pupul">Bolis Pupul</a>宣布了他的首张唱片“Letter To Yu”，并分享了其主打单曲“Completely Half”。看看下面的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlotte-adigery-and-bolis-pupul-share-ceci-nest-pas-un-cliche-detail-us-tour-3150524">夏洛特·阿迪格里 (Charlotte Adigéry) 和波利斯·普普尔 (Bolis Pupul) – 《主题舞者》评论：欢乐、幽默的热潮</a></strong></li></ul><p>《给于的信》被描述为一封写给他2008年因交通事故去世的母亲的情书。普普尔的父亲是比利时人，母亲是中国人。母亲去世后，普普尔开始拥抱并接受他的传统。</p><p> “当我开始思考我的根源时，我不再为它们感到羞耻，而是开始拥抱它们，”他说（根据<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/bolis-pupul-announces-his-soulwax-produced-debut-album-letter-to-yu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>“最适合的线</em></a>”）。 “因此，与他们取得联系对我来说变得越来越重要。我在比利时上夜校并开始学习中文。我这样做了四年。这是第一步。” </p><p><iframe title="Bolis Pupul - Completely Half（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YQfCWB-TOrg?start=3&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Completley Half》的视频由 Magnum 摄影师 Bieke Depoorter 在香港市中心拍摄，视频中 Pupul 探索这座中国城市的街道和建筑物，寻找他已故的母亲。</p><p>谈到创作首张唱片的经历，Pupul 表示（根据<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/bolis-pupul-announces-his-soulwax-produced-debut-album-letter-to-yu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Line of Best Fit</em></a> ）“尽管这次旅行非常激动，有时也很悲伤，但我也度过了一些让我非常开心的美好时光。这产生了非常令人振奋的旋律，让我觉得我可以掌控自己的生活。”</p><p> 《Letter To Yu》将于 3 月 8 日通过<a href="/artists/soulwax">Soulwax</a>的唱片公司 Deewee 发行。比利时电子摇滚二人组与 Pupul 共同制作了这张唱片。<a href="https://bolispupul.lnk.to/letter-to-yu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订专辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0Oqqnutji0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M